original_title: Tim Hawkins: Full Range of Motion
overview: Filmed before a sold out crowd in Dallas, "Full Range of Motion" contains nearly 2 hours of stand up comedy and bonus features: • Tim's full length concert (74 min) • "A Life in the Day" with Tim • Deleted concert scenes • Guest Comedian: Cleto Rodriguez • 5 x 2:00 promotional concert clips
title: Tim Hawkins: Full Range of Motion
